text: Walter Colbath (March 10, 1906 - March 24, 1986) was an American diver. He competed in the men's 10 metre platform event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1906 births Category:1986 deaths Category:American male divers Category:Olympic divers of the United States Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saginaw, Michigan
